{"tid":87682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇眼科醫生？","createTime":"2017-01-20T04:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T10:09:13.000Z","uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9a1872421eed24f4099732cb9baf51b92af426","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"上個月尾比手指整到 個下有痛 第日冇再痛<br />\n係一路睇野濛<br />\n睇完政府醫生同私家開左antibiotic同hypromellose滴過下 但一路blurred vision<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個2個醫生都話cornea傷口好左 仲濛可能近視深左本身<br />\n但明明整親前睇野都清<br />\n上網睇過下外國網 話仲濛會係corneal edema 會用muro128滴 想問自己買黎滴有冇問題 唔想再哂錢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076a67930c27e1bccad59d077e307aca377d0d99","tid":87682,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個月尾比手指整到 個下有痛 第日冇再痛<br />\n係一路睇野濛<br />\n睇完政府醫生同私家開左antibiotic同hypromellose滴過下 但一路blurred vision<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個2個醫生都話cornea傷口好左 仲濛可能近視深左本身<br />\n但明明整親前睇野都清<br />\n上網睇過下外國網 話仲濛會係corneal edema 會用muro128滴 想問自己買黎滴有冇問題 唔想再哂錢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你盲都係抵死<br />\n咁都唔去睇醫生"},{"pid":"f64c39c3be8253ea0cc0105e5e4ce8542be2f1cc","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上個月尾比手指整到 個下有痛 第日冇再痛<br />\n係一路睇野濛<br />\n睇完政府醫生同私家開左antibiotic同hypromellose滴過下 但一路blurred vision<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個2個醫生都話cornea傷口好左 仲濛可能近視深左本身<br />\n但明明整親前睇野都清<br />\n上網睇過下外國網 話仲濛會係corneal edema 會用muro128滴 想問自己買黎滴有冇問題 唔想再哂錢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你盲都係抵死<br />\n咁都唔去睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n屌咪話睇左幾次 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d311851c35acc3d7faeaf54d9a76202170657290","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:42:21.000Z","msg":"前日先睇完私家 就係覺冇用先上黎睇下有冇其他意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694066e71109a7e8f4ee2e68a64b861eadadda01","tid":87682,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"好似未喺連登見過Ophthalmologist <br />\nBTW 你個case 近視深左個機會大過corneal edema"},{"pid":"f9cfc75a41b608627d85bcb6641c87056a85991f","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似未喺連登見過Ophthalmologist <br />\nBTW 你個case 近視深左個機會大過corneal edema</blockquote><br />\n但我睇外國網都幾多係corneal abrasion 滴完muro128清返 有啲就自己好返<br />\n我好確定未整親前係冇咁深近視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dbc7155fbbbcced60a2d8b9332023ff1eaf7d8","tid":87682,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似未喺連登見過Ophthalmologist <br />\nBTW 你個case 近視深左個機會大過corneal edema</blockquote><br />\n但我睇外國網都幾多係corneal abrasion 滴完muro128清返 有啲就自己好返<br />\n我好確定未整親前係冇咁深近視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解唔去Check 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你期望喺呢度搵到咩答案"},{"pid":"afbe63acca5cfe1558df2caa69dffee6e94c33c2","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似未喺連登見過Ophthalmologist <br />\nBTW 你個case 近視深左個機會大過corneal edema</blockquote><br />\n但我睇外國網都幾多係corneal abrasion 滴完muro128清返 有啲就自己好返<br />\n我好確定未整親前係冇咁深近視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解唔去Check 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你期望喺呢度搵到咩答案</blockquote><br />\n我睇左幾次 前日先睇完 但一路冇改善<br />\n都話個wound好左 濛係近視深左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係睇下有冇眼科醫生會上連登拎下意見姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92460715301d246bb2b7b5f4c97c987d9f6e3ab0","tid":87682,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"第一，點解醫生會話「可能」深左，明明好簡單就Check 到，你又唔去做<br />\n第二，上網做到診斷就唔使睇醫生啦，你所講嘅Corneal edema 擺上顯微鏡睇實睇到，同埋要好嚴重先會影響視力，係好微機會"},{"pid":"2f3331b321b7442f1d7214a178e23a50e43577fb","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一，點解醫生會話「可能」深左，明明好簡單就Check 到，你又唔去做<br />\n第二，上網做到診斷就唔使睇醫生啦，你所講嘅Corneal edema 擺上顯微鏡睇實睇到，同埋要好嚴重先會影響視力，係好微機會</blockquote><br />\n前日睇佢有驗眼<br />\n本身右眼不嬲200幾度<br />\n前日度完變左400幾度<br />\n但左眼依然200幾冇變"},{"pid":"77637a524cd42df35105f4a2a5dc64cbf24df9e9","tid":87682,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一，點解醫生會話「可能」深左，明明好簡單就Check 到，你又唔去做<br />\n第二，上網做到診斷就唔使睇醫生啦，你所講嘅Corneal edema 擺上顯微鏡睇實睇到，同埋要好嚴重先會影響視力，係好微機會</blockquote><br />\n前日睇佢有驗眼<br />\n本身右眼不嬲200幾度<br />\n前日度完變左400幾度<br />\n但左眼依然200幾冇變</blockquote><br />\n你不如再去Seek another professional advice"},{"pid":"8586cd52520b26380fa28381a958032a7c1680e6","tid":87682,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"唔信醫生但信網上資訊<br />\n咁我自己google都做到醫生啦，班醫生讀咁多年書讀屎片"},{"pid":"efd29724212fff8e50d65d16aa8d0655ed4918ed","tid":87682,"uid":7754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"眼科專科醫生啱唔啱？"},{"pid":"57e6d13229b2a002aed1b33e5c8d96c87d1ac7b8","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔信醫生但信網上資訊<br />\n咁我自己google都做到醫生啦，班醫生讀咁多年書讀屎片</blockquote><br />\n但佢地都話只係近視深左<br />\n屌但我明明整親前帶眼鏡係超清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8fe407f39aa2a355d2e2d7c99d112573b3c64e","tid":87682,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔信醫生但信網上資訊<br />\n咁我自己google都做到醫生啦，班醫生讀咁多年書讀屎片</blockquote><br />\n但佢地都話只係近視深左<br />\n屌但我明明整親前帶眼鏡係超清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你整親隻眼得呢2個醫生做過檢查<br />\n就算有眼科醫生喺連登都到唔到意見架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔信佢地既話不如睇多幾個眼科醫生啦"},{"pid":"daf318cea5d75f22c1785f98537c68de75157ab4","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔信醫生但信網上資訊<br />\n咁我自己google都做到醫生啦，班醫生讀咁多年書讀屎片</blockquote><br />\n但佢地都話只係近視深左<br />\n屌但我明明整親前帶眼鏡係超清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你整親隻眼得呢2個醫生做過檢查<br />\n就算有眼科醫生喺連登都到唔到意見架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔信佢地既話不如睇多幾個眼科醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n唉好啦唯有比錢再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad8035e6c334560f0ff0fbc7f1e8c2ef59962f9","tid":87682,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"不過其實如果你無Active infection 睇Ophthalmologist 有啲哂錢"},{"pid":"e0b6e7cb1918f02508ca60bfef35f2c426e55e27","tid":87682,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過其實如果你無Active infection 睇Ophthalmologist 有啲哂錢</blockquote><br />\n冇啦 冇痛冇紅冇腫 整親第日已經滴夠一星期antibiotic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952b60a4a93aabac2e9ac03802be6b3d91157d96","tid":87682,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0d7d98d9ad93a9856de730d8b988bd7fed70608","tid":87682,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53a822566ff6e03ea5ccc06c9555ada50fd04c1f","tid":87682,"